ingredients.ingredient: 1 pound (at least 80%) ground beef, cooked, drained
1 ½ cups Old El Paso® Thick 'n Chunky Salsa
1 (16.3 ounce) can Pillsbury® Grands!® refrigerated biscuits
½ cup shredded Monterey Jack cheese or Mexican cheese blend

cookingTips: Flatten biscuits slightly before adding filling
Drain excess salsa to prevent soggy biscuits
Top with cheese before baking for best melt
